            </p>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <!-- 금단증상 내용 -->
      <div class="symp_contents_wrap">
        <!-- 4D 금단증상 내용 -->
        <div class="symp_contents_4D active">
          <h2>Keep this in mind. "4D", the patience of smoking!</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <div class="contents_upper">
                <div class="contents_img_wrap">
                  <img src="./images/symptom_2.png" alt="symptom_img" />
                </div>
                <p>Delay</p>
              </div>
              <div class="contents_under">
                <p>
                  The desire to smoke lasts for three to five minutes. Try to
                  delay time, such as eating snacks, meditating, etc.
                </p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <div class="contents_upper">
                <div class="contents_img_wrap">
                  <img src="./images/symptom_3.png" alt="symptom_img" />
                </div>
                <p>Drink</p>
              </div>
              <div class="contents_under">
                <p>
                  Sufficient water intake reduces the desire to smoke and lowers
                  the nicotine concentration.
                </p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <div class="contents_upper">
                <div class="contents_img_wrap">
                  <img src="./images/symptom_4.png" alt="symptom_img" />
                </div>
                <p>Do something different</p>
              </div>
              <div class="contents_under">
                <p>
                  If you focus on other things, you can get distracted and
                  forget about smoking.Start something else.
                </p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <div class="contents_upper">
                <div class="contents_img_wrap">
                  <img src="./images/symptom_5.png" alt="symptom_img" />
                </div>
                <p>Deep breathing</p>
              </div>
              <div class="contents_under">
                <p>Take a deep breath to relieve your stress.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <!-- 4D가 아닌 금단증상 내용 -->
        <div class="symp_contents_exception_4D">
          <h2></h2>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <div class="contents_upper">
                <div class="contents_img_wrap">
                  <img src="./images/symptom_6.png" alt="symptom_img" />
                </div>
                <p>Symptom</p>
              </div>
              <div class="contents_under">
                <p></p>
